data.description: Discover comfort and charm in this thoughtfully designed ranch-style home nestled on a picturesque lot. The master suite graces the southern wing, while two bedrooms and a bath occupy the opposite side, offering a balanced layout. A spacious living room seamlessly connects with the family room, kitchen, and dining area, creating a harmonious living environment. Step from the family room onto a generous deck, perfect for relaxation and gatherings.
